"(conseillé)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:711
msgid "IP address"
msgstr "Adresse IP"

#: views/admin-settings.php:711
msgid ""
"A salted hash is irreversible but still counts unique consents. Your server "
"already logs IPs."
msgstr ""
"Un hachage salé est irréversible tout en permettant de comptabiliser les "
"consentements uniques. Votre serveur enregistre déjà les IP."

#: views/admin-settings.php:713
msgid "Salted hash (recommended)"
msgstr "Hachage salé (recommandé)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:713
msgid "Full IP"
msgstr "IP complète"

#: views/admin-settings.php:716
msgid "User-agent"
msgstr "User-agent"

#: views/admin-settings.php:717
msgid "Record the browser user-agent string"
msgstr "Enregistrer la chaîne user-agent du navigateur"

#: views/admin-settings.php:719
msgid "Record the logged-in user (guests are never identified)"
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer l’utilisateur connecté (les invités ne sont jamais identifiés)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:720
msgid "Retention (days)"
msgstr "Conservation (jours)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:721
msgid "0 = keep forever"
msgstr "0 = conserver indéfiniment"

#: views/admin-settings.php:722
msgid ""
"Proof should be kept at least as long as the consent lasts, or you may "
"delete evidence for valid consents."
msgstr ""
"La preuve doit être conservée au moins aussi longtemps que dure le "
"consentement, sinon vous risquez de supprimer des preuves pour des "
"consentements valides."

#: views/admin-settings.php:723
msgid "On uninstall"
msgstr "À la désinstallation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:723
msgid ""
"Keep the proof after uninstalling for legal accountability — re-installing "
"later reuses it."
msgstr ""
"Conserver la preuve après la désinstallation pour la responsabilité légale — "
"une réinstallation ultérieure la réutilise."

#: views/admin-settings.php:724
msgid "Keep the consent log when uninstalling"
msgstr "Conserver le journal de consentement à la désinstallation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:731
msgid "Save all settings"
msgstr "Enregistrer tous les réglages"

#: views/admin-settings.php:732
msgid "One save applies to every tab."
msgstr "Un seul enregistrement s’applique à tous les onglets."

#: views/admin-settings.php:740
msgid "Consent log cleared."
msgstr "Journal de consentement effacé."

